(359, 1767, 217, 117, '1', 'upload/217//customer_profile_document/M0rpz2nOtLt1aERnOrmi9nO0W8kOIcPROBLEM_STATEMENT.docx', 'Revolutionizing Security: Portable Synthetic Immune sistem (PSI) against Bioterrorism and Extraterrestrial Threats', 'The Portable Synthetic Immune System offers a unique and effective solution for countering bioterrorist attacks and promoting human survival in space. Our products are highly specific, effective, and affordable, making them a valuable addition to government agencies, defense organizations, space exploration, and colonization companies, and healthcare providers. With our cutting-edge technology and expertise in biotechnology, we provide reliable and innovative solutions.\r\n   Survival in extreme environments: The space exploration and colonization industry needs solutions that can help support human life in harsh and extreme environments such as outer space.\r\n    Specificity and effectiveness: Synthetic antibodies that are highly specific and effective in neutralizing targeted biothreats and medical conditions.\r\n    Cost-effectiveness: Affordable solutions that can provide maximum protection and support with minimal costs.\r\n', 0, 1, '2023-03-10 13:43:41', '2023-03-10 14:07:22'),
